data.description: Fantastic opportunity to own this bright, sunny, and beautiful 3-bedroom condo with a desirable open floor plan features of three separate bedrooms with all walk in closet and two full baths.   This light-filled unit has been freshly painted throughout, brand new dishwasher, window treatment and new lighting fixtures. The kitchen cabinet has been completely upgraded. The Master Bedroom is an oasis, featuring an ensuite bath complete with a separate shower, soaking tub, and a dual vanity -  rejoice!  Conveys with private detached garage parking space.   The incredible location within walking distance to the Village at Leesburg, immediately accessible to Rt 7.   This is a pet-friendly haven where your furry companions are welcomed with open arms. Situated conveniently close to upscale shopping, fine dining, and entertainment options, this location is a dream come true.
